# **错误** 激活simple framebuffer，会导致NVIDIA编译提示错误，并且花屏
Device Drivers --->
   Firmware Drivers  --->
      [*] Mark VGA/VBE/EFI FB as generic system framebuffer
   Graphics support --->
      <*> Simple framebuffer support #这个选项要求 "Direct Rendering Manager (XFree86 4.1.0 and higher DRI support)" 也编译成build-in，否则只能module
